'desc': [u'

Piyo Piyo Weaning Tableware Set Price: Rs.605

Having sufficient amount of tableware on the dining table is very important so as to make mealtime easy
column17:
convenient and fun. The Weaning Tableware Set is exclusively designed for kids so as to smoothly and comfortably take them through their weaning stage.

\r\n

\r\n\tThis Tableware Set from Piyo Piyo comprises of 1 Juice or Soup Spoon
column21: 1 Fresh Lid and 1 Dining Tray. Use these containers to carefully feed your baby as he learns to swallow and digest solid and semi-solid foods. All these containers are made to be Cold and Heat Resistant so that they do not get damaged easily in extreme conditions. The Bowls are Microwaveable and feature Slip-Proof Grips so as to make it convenient to feed your baby. The spoons have soft tips to get the babies accustomed to their touch. The Dining Tray
column22:
Bowl and Spoon Grip are all made out of Polypropylene Material for increased durability and can be used for both girls and boys.

\n
\n ']

column4: 'title': [u'\n                    Piyo Piyo 4 Stage Training Cup Set            ']
column16:
'desc': [u'

Piyo Piyo 4 Stage Training Cup Set Price: Rs.989

During the growth period of babies
column17: they are under a constant learning process and get exposed to new things every day. As you start feeding the baby with a bottle
column18:
it is important that they should learn the right technique for it so as to avoid spillage and wastage.

\r\n

\r\n\tThe 4 Stage Training Cup Set from Piyo Piyo is a set which will help you train your baby for all these different activities. This set includes a Training Cup with One Nipple Style Lid for the baby to smoothly transit from breast feeding to bottle feeding. Along with this
column19: the Training Cup Set provides you with a Duck-billed Lid
column20: One Straw Style Lid and One Broad-Opening Lid. The cup in this training set is made out of Polypropylene Material for increased durability and has a Silicone Watertight Ring. The Thermoplastic Rubber Handles of this cup are made to be Skid-Proof so that it is easy for the baby to drink from it independently. Babies belonging to the age group of 3 months to 1 year can be trained using this Piyo Piyo Training Set. This training set is simple
column21:
easy-to-use and can be used for both girls and boys.

\n
\n ']
